@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_trlipa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v0 * tmp)
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.57)) * v2)
    v0 = (0.94 + wp.abs((v1 + 0.28 / tmp + 0.95)))
    v2 = (v2 - (wp.abs(v2 + 0.13) * wp.sin(tmp + 0.57)))
    v1 = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.66 * v0 + 0.49) + v0))
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = 0.49
    data[tid] = v0
